            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>grated carrot </strong>to the <strong>gochujang dressing</strong> with the<strong> spring onion strips </strong>and <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>gochujang slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1653319790279-x200.jpg",
